00:00:26,026 --> 00:00:30,190
WEDNESDAY, FEBRUARY 5, 1975

3
00:00:39,081 --> 00:00:45,703
THE LOST HONOUR OF KATHARINA BLUM

4
00:04:15,255 --> 00:04:18,543
Hello, Katharina?
