929
01:45:32,576 --> 01:45:35,034
CHARACTERS AND EVENTS ARE FICTITIOUS

930
01:45:35,162 --> 01:45:37,699
DESCRIPTION OF
CERTAIN JOURNALISTIC PRACTICES

931
01:45:37,832 --> 01:45:40,324
